features: 【COFFEE TABLE WITH STORAGE】The coffee table includes a double-sided wooden drawer and an open storage space. You can put some important documents, pens, CDs, toys in the drawer, which acts as a dust barrier. You can easily store and grab books, magazines, snacks, phones, or board games in the open storage space. In addition, you can place anything on top of your desk, including plants, photos, a TV, a projector and a fruit tray.

【VERSATILE AND MULTIFUNCTIONAL TABLE】The coffee table can be not only a floating entertainment center but also a TV stand, both simple and stylish, with a modern style that can match your various furniture and make your room neat, organised and elegant. The coffee table is suitable for many places, such as the living room, bedroom, office, study, hallway or entrance.

【EASY TO CLEAN AND ASSEMBLE】The coffee table has a waterproof surface, smooth and detailed material and an open interior that can be easily wiped down with just a damp rag to keep it clean. In addition, the package contains all the assembly kits, table parts and detailed instructions. Therefore, following the instructions will not take long.

【WOOD COFFEE TABLE】Made from strong and durable high quality chipboard, the coffee table is supported on its base by four solid rubber woods, screwed and dowelled for extra stability, with a high load-bearing capacity and will last longer, being not only environmentally friendly but also odourless. So buy with confidence.

【COFFEE TABLE DIMENSION】The overall dimensions of the coffee table ： 39.33" W x 19.44" D x 16.43" H. Leg height is 7.1 in (18 cm). Our Cozy Castle is a 365-day good companion for any problem. Any question? Please do not hesitate to let us know and solve them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 3, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great table, but my shipment had defects; seller addressed them.
reviews.reviewText: There was a very similar, nearly identical table on Wayfair, but it was $125.99, so I went for this one, which was $89.99 at the time of this review. I love the minimalist and modern look of the table. Another plus is that the drawer can be opened from either side, and can also be placed in either compartment.The reason I want to give this particular product 3 stars is because it had several defects upon delivery. One of the wooden pegs was decayed and missing a chunk. One of the two big panels had scratches on the side (and they would be visible after assembly). The other panel had some warping/bubbling on one of the edges as well, and it sort of looked like water damage. Lastly, one of the holes in the panel was missing a rubber ring that had to be in there in order for the pegs to fit in snugly. We ended up assembling the table without that third peg, and it seems fine, though it makes me nervous that essentially 33% of the reinforcement is missing. Lastly, the product had clearly been used previously, as there were streaks and weird marks on the panel that I think was used as the table top.Upon bringing these issues to the attention of the seller and asking for a partial or full refund, they offered me 20%, which I thought was low—I paid for a new table, but I got a clearly used one with several defects. They then offered 50% and I accepted. I appreciate their customer service and attentiveness, and it’s the key reason I’m not giving them a 2 or 3 star rating.Originally, I purchased it on June 29 and received it on July 1, despite the original delivery estimate saying July 2-8. It always took less than 24 hours to hear back from the seller as well, and they addressed all my concerns well, so I’m bumping it up to 4.
